'''Akarere ka Burera''' ni kamwe mu turere dutanu (5) tugize intara y'amajyaruguru,kashyizweho n'itegeko N029/2005 yo ku wa23/12/2005 rijyanye no gushyiraho uturere tw'u Rwanda Icyicaro cyako kiri ahitwa Kirambo

Akarere ka Burera kagizwe n'[[Imirenge y’u Rwanda|imirenge]] 17 ariyo: [[Umurenge wa Bungwe|Bungwe]], [[Umurenge wa Butaro|Butaro]], [[Umurenge wa Cyanika|Cyanika]], [[Umurenge wa Cyeru|Cyeru]], [[Umurenge wa Gahunga|Gahunga]], [[Umurenge wa Gatebe|Gatebe]], [[Umurenge wa Gitovu|Gitovu]], [[Umurenge wa Kagogo|Kagogo]], [[Umurenge wa Kinoni|Kinoni]], [[Umurenge wa Kinyababa|Kinyababa]], [[Umurenge wa Kivuye|Kivuye]], [[Umurenge wa Nemba|Nemba]], [[Umurenge wa Rugarama|Rugarama]], [[Umurenge wa Rugengabari|Rugengabari]], [[Umurenge wa Ruhunde|Ruhunde]], [[Umurenge wa Rusarabuye|Rusarabuye]] na [[Umurenge wa Rwerere|Rwerere]]. [[Utugari]] ni 69, [[imidugudu]] ni 571. Abaturage bose ni 325988. Abarengeje imyaka 18 ni 150.009

Gahana imbibi na:

:Mu majyaruguru: Igihugu cya Uganda
:Mu Majyepfo: [[Akarere ka Gakenke]] na [[Akarere ka Rulindo|Rulindo]].
:Iburasirazuba: [[Akarere ka Gicumbi]].
:Iburengerazuba: [[Akarere ka Musanze]].

